                              <p className="font-semibold text-gray-900">{plane.name}</p>
                              <p className="text-gray-700 text-sm">{plane.description}</p>
                            </div>
                          ))}
                          <p className="text-yellow-900 font-semibold mt-3">
                            This indicates a supplementary marriage - you are stronger together than apart. This is a karmic relationship designed for mutual growth.
                          </p>
                        </div>
                      )}
                      
                      <div className="bg-green-100 border border-green-400 p-3 rounded mt-3">
                        <p className="text-green-900 font-semibold">💑 Marriage Wisdom:</p>
                        <p className="text-green-800 text-sm">
                          Your spouse completes what you lack. This is called a "Supplementary Marriage" in numerology - where each partner's strengths balance the other's weaknesses. 
                          Such marriages, though they may have challenges, are designed for tremendous personal growth and are often karmic connections meant to teach important life lessons.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                )}
              </div>
            )}

            {/* Priority-Based Remedies */}
            {results.missing.length > 0 && (
              <div className="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-6">
                <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold text-red-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <AlertCircle />
                  Complete Remedy Guide (Priority-Based)
                </h2>

                <div className="bg-yellow-50 border-l
